functionToggleGod()
if(notgod)then
god=1;
elsegod=1-god;
end
if(god==1)then
Hud:AddMessage("[CHEAT]:God-ModeON");
System:LogToConsole("God-ModeON");
else
Hud:AddMessage("[CHEAT]:God-ModeOFF");
System:LogToConsole("God-ModeOFF");
end
end
Input:BindCommandToKey("#ToggleGod()","backspace",1);
